00:34:27,028 --> 00:34:29,728
As minhas mãos.
Toma, partilhem.

497
00:34:38,001 --> 00:34:39,740
<i>Nível de oxigénio crítico.</i>

498
00:34:40,278 --> 00:34:42,228
