507
00:35:32,991 --> 00:35:34,874
O disjuntor. Vira-o.

508
00:35:34,904 --> 00:35:36,604
Muito bem, espera.

509
00:36:10,363 --> 00:36:11,813
Já está.

510
00:36:15,062 --> 00:36:16,062
Vamos.

511
00:36:57,912 --> 00:36:59,962
Ela salvou-nos outra vez.

512
00:37:05,149 --> 00:37:07,899
